Fig. 23. Variation of ventral color pattern in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dunn" authorityYear="1949" box="[646,862,1211,1231]" class="Amphibia" family="Microhylidae" genus="Chiasmocleis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Anura" pageId="41" pageNumber="41" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bassleri">
<emphasis box="[646,862,1211,1231]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="41">Chiasmocleis bassleri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. (
<emphasis bold="true" box="[885,903,1212,1231]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41">A</emphasis>
) Parque Nacional da Serra do Divisor, Acre, Brazil (UFAC-RB 1611). (
<emphasis bold="true" box="[554,570,1239,1258]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41">B</emphasis>
