<emphasis bold="true" box="[1203,1219,1265,1284]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41">E</emphasis>
) Floresta Nacional do Pau-Rosa, Rio Paraconi, Maués, Amazonas, Brazil (MPEG 27766). (
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1091,1106,1292,1311]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41">F</emphasis>
) Aripuanã, Mato Grosso, Brazil (UFMT 7136). Not to scale.
</paragraph>
